            <H2>How Do I Get to and From Terminal A? </H2>
            <p>Getting to and from the new Terminal A is well-integrated with the Newark Airport transport system. AirTrain Newark is a free and automated monorail system that connects all of EWR's terminals (A, B, C), parking lots, and the Newark Liberty International Airport Station. </p>
